Package: pamir-ai-eink-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         dkms,
         device-tree-compiler,
         linux-headers-rpi-2712
Recommends: pamir-ai-eink-tests
Suggests:
Description: Pamir AI E-Ink Display Driver (DKMS)
 This package provides a DKMS (Dynamic Kernel Module Support) driver
 for Pamir AI E-Ink displays using the SSD1681 controller.
 .
 Features:
  - Support for 128x250 monochrome E-Ink displays
  - Multiple update modes (full, partial, base map)
  - Framebuffer interface (/dev/fb0)
  - Sysfs control interface
  - IOCTL control for advanced features
  - Deep sleep mode for power efficiency
 .
 Compatible with Raspberry Pi CM5 and other SPI-enabled devices.

Package: pamir-ai-eink-tests
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         python3,
         python3-pil,
         python3-requests
Description: Test programs for Pamir AI E-Ink Display Driver
 This package provides test programs and examples for the Pamir AI
 E-Ink display driver, including:
 .
  - Real-time clock display
  - Weather dashboard
  - System monitor with graphs
  - E-book reader
  - Various demonstration programs
 .
 Test programs are installed to /opt/distiller-eink-tests/
